title: Greg Graffin Live at CSUN April/27/1998
description:
Greg Graffin Live at Cal State University Northridge CSUN April/27/1998

Long awaited live audio of Graffins AL tour

Sorry I dont have the good date with the setlist that has billy and whatnot. This one
still kicks bum.

001 Setlist
 
01 Intro! welcome to cal state!
02 God song
03 Fault line*
04 Opinion*
05 Suffer
----Greg hops off guitar and onto piano all songs below are piano
06 Get off
07 Back to earth*
08 Cease*
09 Best for you
10 Predicament*
 
*= American Lesion songs(yep I count cease)

9 songs+chat = 40min 

Unedited version and a simple noise reduce for the horrid tape hiss makes a C- show imo
